sentences.sentence: The setting up of STET Centre is not expected to have any material impact on the consolidated net tangible assets per share and earnings per share of ST Engineering for the current financial year.
sentences.translation: 新加坡科技工程有限公司并没有期望通过STET中心的建立对其本财政年度的整体每股有形资产净值和每股收益产生实质性的影响。
